                        <head>55. Minutes of a Working Group Meeting<note n="1" type="source" xml:id="d55fn1">Source: Reagan Library, System IV Intelligence
                                Files, 1988, Unnumbered Notebook 1 of 2, 1988. Top Secret; [<hi rend="italic">handling restriction not declassified</hi>]. The
                                meeting took place in Room 208 of the Old Executive Office
                                Building.</note></head>
                        <opener><dateline rendition="#right"><placeName>Washington</placeName>,
                                    <date calendar="gregorian" from="1988-04-15T14:00:00-04:00" to="1988-04-15T15:30:00-04:00">April 15, 1988, 2–3:30
                                    p.m.</date></dateline></opener>
                        <!--<pb facs="d55-2" n="2" type="facsimile" xml:id="d55-2"/>-->
